'''Maiduguri International Airport''' {{airport codes|MIU|DNMA}} is an airport serving [[Maiduguri]], the capital of [[Borno State]] in [[Nigeria]].
The runway length does not include a {{convert|120|m}} [[displaced threshold]] on each end.
